title: Packers-Lions MNF Preview, Dan Quinn's hot seat and Chiefs concerns (Football 10/14)
description:
Will Brinson and Jared Dubin preview Monday night's Packers-Lions game [0:38] and then Jason La Canfora joins Will to talk about the latest news from around the NFL [24:13], including the hot seat for Dan Quinn [27:35], the Chiefs struggles [37:30], the Cowboys play calling [52:35] and the Vikings resurgence plus much more [54:10].
